# BiB Metabolomics {#BiB_Metabolomics}


Nuclear magnetic resonance (NMR) and mass spectrometry (MS) metabolomics on BiB pregnancy, neonatal and infant samples.



## MS metabolomics paired mother samples scaled {#BiB_Metabolomics.metms_pairm_s}


Mass spectrometry metabolomics (Metabolon) with over 1300 markers from mother pregnancy bloods. Paired neonatal sample data also available. Scaled values.
